11
00:00:30,415 --> 00:00:32,083
U.S. President Andrew Jackson

12
00:00:32,084 --> 00:00:34,051
is hesitant to intervene,

13
00:00:34,052 --> 00:00:35,635
and Texas has no choice

14
00:00:35,637 --> 00:00:40,174
but to declare itself
an independent nation.

15
00:00:40,175 --> 00:00:42,325
Outnumbered, General Sam Houston's

16
00:00:42,344 --> 00:00:44,011
Texas Republic Army

17
00:00:44,012 --> 00:00:46,496
and Steve Austin's Ranging Company

18
00:00:46,515 --> 00:00:49,183
are all that stand between
Santa Anna's tyranny

19
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:50,684
and independence.

20
00:00:50,685 --> 00:00:54,087
Texas in flames; the Alamo in ashes.

21
00:00:54,089 --> 00:00:56,574
Pioneers, Mexicans, Tejanos,

22
