Let them tell their
drunken General Houston

82
00:05:04,939 --> 00:05:06,940
the stories of our triumph.

83
00:05:06,941 --> 00:05:08,541
Excellent.

84
00:05:10,111 --> 00:05:12,446
Ride to General Urrea's battalion,

85
00:05:12,447 --> 00:05:16,283
and order him to attack
Fort Goliad without delay.

86
00:05:16,284 --> 00:05:17,383
[grunts]

87
00:05:22,957 --> 00:05:26,275
[baby crying]

88
00:05:29,097 --> 00:05:32,198
[baby crying]

89
